                &lt;code&gt;MouseInfo&lt;/code&gt;  provides methods for getting information about the mouse,
                  such as mouse pointer location and the number of mouse buttons.                
                <author>
                    Roman Poborchiy                    
                </author>
                <since>
                    1.5                    
                </since>
            </javadoc>
